msgstr "ドワーフのベルト"

#. [object]: id=DwarvenBelt
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/06b_In_the_Domain_of_Dwarves.cfg:1687
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios_old/06b_In_the_Domain_of_Dwarves.cfg:1687
