#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/08_Out_of_the_Frying_Pan.cfg:1322
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios_old/08_Out_of_the_Frying_Pan.cfg:1305
