#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios_old/09_Blood_is_Thicker_Than_Water.cfg:552
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios_old/09_Blood_is_Thicker_Than_Water.cfg:553
